Want 100% natural & fresh hispanic desserts and yummy treats.
Come here!
Its my husbands favorite.. and he's from El Paso, Tx.
WARNING; No english speaking people or workers available!
Come with translator or good fingers to point items out.
Our favorites;  Elote En Vaso (corn in a cup with butter, mayo, cheese & hot sauce) medium $3 & large $ 5   Magonadas  $3 (frozen mango juice w/brown sugar in a sauce)   Banana Split $5 (different ice cream flavors w/banana, whip & toppings)  They have other delectable treats such as;  - Licuados (shakes) - cocos frescos  - chocolate covered bananas $3 - paletas (fruit ice cream bars) - manzanas decoradas (candy apples) - nachos  small; $1.50 large; $3 - churros $1  PLUS LOTS LOTS MORE!

